{"type": "article", "id": 37289, "title": "Tod's 业绩不佳，以及， Lemaire 与优衣库的合作款又来了 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-26T04:53:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 2211, "name": "Tod's"}, {"id": 15623, "name": "Gosha Rubchinskiy"}, {"id": 15798, "name": "NEIGHBORHOOD"}, {"id": 28551, "name": "Champion"}, {"id": 7576, "name": "Christophe Lemaire"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170126105836k6jogQmvn7DwXtz8.png", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/tods-results-idUSI6N1FA001\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>意大利奢侈品牌 Tod’s，2016 年业绩低迷</b></a> | 尽管 Tod’s 在去年的最后一个季度的业绩有所上升，不过，它的核心业务鞋类和皮革制品在最主要的两个市场——美国和中国的表现不佳，由此拖累了 Tod’s 集团在 2016 年全年，销售额同比下跌了 3.6%，至 10.8 亿美元。&nbsp;</p><p><b><a href=\"http://luxe.co/post/53980/\" rel=\"nofollow\">消费品私募基金 L Catterton 联手超模 Karlie Kloss 等名人，投资了一个新兴的椰子油品牌 Kopari Beauty</a></b> | 该品牌于 2015 年创办于圣地亚哥，品牌产品以椰子油为基础，品类涵盖了洁面、面霜、精华、身体乳、唇膏等。据业内估计，Kopari Beauty 2016年销售额应该在 500 万美元左右。这笔投资将用来进一步提升该品牌知名度，扩大销售市场和产品品类。&nbsp;<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\">还记得爱马仕的前任创意总监 </font>Christophe Lemaire 与优衣库的合作款吗？这个系列曾经帮助优衣库在商业上取得了巨大的成功。在<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/uniqlo-christophe-lemaire-uniqlo-u-2017-651\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 2017 春夏，Christophe Lemaire 再度发布了与优衣库的合作系列</a>。该系列继续以优衣库的 LifeWear 为原型，选用了湖水蓝、橄榄绿这样的颜色来代表 Lemaire 的优雅，在剪裁上也更为细腻和更富层次感了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 50); font-size: large;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112042LXwtKWAUcpHD9sTo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112045xhmeMAoqkHWSvPsI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701261120477mEDKeolQBJAIUW4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112050Ss8lHdqxQJP4hIEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112052akrcIonx3VBRwNGD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112055WMO83EmtInlKZh5x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112056ZXQrBH3glKCGPdv7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112056OJpz3ghlmYIbAGHM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112059ozgsM6tHcTifB0rX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112101CR8idgqkGw6PcBI9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112101iTSfZdgvj0GLD5N4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112101sYD9Nj5v8Ryfaw4W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 50); font-size: large;\">日本潮牌</span><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/neighborhood-2017-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Neighborhood 发布了 2017 春夏系列 lookbook</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 50); font-size: large;\">，该系列渗透了品牌多年来的军事、工装、牛仔及机车元素，将于 2 月 4 日正式发售。</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\"></font><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701261121205IB40ZfWHsycwmpl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112126g1dfZ2JGOVC9ehUE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112126QIhLejvBy9rW2fP8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112128X9fwEe7PjhMB8vUO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112129enNzA9Lv5uOjRJUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112130XGUjvzLqRQ7AxChm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112154uQenPp3WiodBFRKC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112200GjCv89BPwglV5TIo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017012611220414CxkYu8BZDILTA9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112221xfrBjsi43EubM7Pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112231DIyNwZ0QYcAdpSuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\">意大利品牌 </font><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/casbia-champion-awol-atlanta\" rel=\"nofollow\"><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\">CASBIA 与 Champion 合作，带来了联名款 </font>AWOL Atlanta 球鞋</a>。首发黑、白两色，均以高档皮革制作，并搭配了不对称金属拉链更方便穿着，在后侧与外底处以 Champion 的 logo 作点缀。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112256wca6sSRVWCAtfYz5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701261123002uZfwnNlXbg8EDqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112343DScgbX6ZxBMu9EwH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017012611234624hmCxRMzFGvjosp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>上次我们曾写过，代表后苏维埃风格的 Gosha Rubchinskiy 在 2017 年秋冬系列邀来了 adidas 一起走秀。秀场上除了合作的衣服之外，以足球靴 ACE 16+ 作为蓝本改造的联名鞋款同样备受瞩目。来看这双足球靴 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/gosha-rubchinskiy-x-adidas-football-ace-16-hybrid-more-details\" rel=\"nofollow\">ACE 16+ super </a>的更多细节：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112543jzv56N3QqEcBroxT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126112625VdFRLGbMzg9K3C48.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">洛杉矶街头潮牌&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">STAMPD 与日本品牌 Monkey T</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">ime 合作，推出了以 70 年代英国亚文化为灵感的系列。包括工服、帽衫、T 恤、破洞牛仔裤等，破坏做旧处理搭配颇有极简感的街头风很好看。</span>STAMPD官网将在 1 月 27 号出售此系列。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126114632HY1puF7PtxGUy5ED.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126114632osxA9e4iyLPrfhRa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126114634h87acQDsufJkpPRg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126114631THt7gU5xzjWRADrG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126114630eR1C2mWi7lwTOXop.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126114630svLN0dxXIR1D4g5m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170126114631wQ1kpjY6AUWig5rL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px 'Yuanti SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px 'Yuanti SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/neighborhood-2017-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">hypebeast</a><br></p>"}